snippet.title: SafeZoneVR Environment Display | Release Date
snippet.description:
SafeZoneVR Environment Display | Launch Date  **Gameplay experience spoilers included**

**If you plan on playing the game, for the best experience avoid this video as it shows off some of the areas and environments in the game.

SafeZoneVR Official Trailer | Free Survival Game
Itch.io page: https://will-codes.itch.io/safe-zone​

UploadVR Article: https://uploadvr.com/safezonevr-upcom...

What is it?
SafeZoneVR is a VR horror game coming soon free to pc VR. This immersive, ultra-realistic game will make you live the storyline inside of this game. The game has been in development for nearly 3 years and will be releasing in 2021

Please leave all feedback in the comments below I will reply to every comment!
